 pandemic and the poor • Calibrating covid risk • Russia’s rotten statistics</p></div><div itemscope="" itemProp="image" itemType="https://schema.org/ImageObject" class="teaser__image"><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.economist.com/sites/default/files/newheader2_1_0.png"/><img src="https://www.economist.com/sites/default/files/newheader2_1_0.png" srcSet="https://www.economist.com/img/b/200/113/90/sites/default/files/newheader2_1_0.png 200w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/300/169/90/sites/default/files/newheader2_1_0.png 300w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/400/225/90/sites/default/files/newheader2_1_0.png 400w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/600/338/90/sites/default/files/newheader2_1_0.png 600w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/640/360/90/sites/default/files/newheader2_1_0.png 640w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/800/450/90/sites/default/files/newheader2_1_0.png 800w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/1000/563/90/sites/default/files/newheader2_1_0.png 1000w,https://www.economist.com/img/b/1280/720/90/sites/default/files/newheader2_1_0.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 320px) 300px, (max-width: 414px) 400px, (max-width: 600px) 640px, (max-width: 768px) 800px, (max-width: 960px) 1000px, (max-width: 1024px) 1200px" alt=""/></div></div></div><div class="layout-moreover"><strong class="ds-section-headline ds-section-headline--rule-emphasised">Moreover</strong><div data-test-id="Article Teaser" class="teaser"><div class="teaser__text"><a class="section-fly" href="/books-and-arts/">Books &amp; arts</a><h3><a class="headline-link" href="/books-and-arts/2020/05/23/trio-sonatas-are-the-ideal-music-for-the-lockdown"><span class="teaser__headline teaser__headline--sc3">Trio sonatas are the ideal music for the lockdown</span></a></h3><p data-test-id="Description" itemProp="description" class="teaser__description teaser__description--sc2">Warm and uplifting, they are built for the spare room, not the concert hall</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="ds-slim-med